    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"essence\" and \"elegance\" don't really show up on the bottom line though. templates are way cheaper and they won't hallucinate or go off-script. if we can hit our basic KPIs with them, the company is happy. honestly, it's better for the workflow if we just stick to the scripts. isn't it easier to just follow a pre-set path?",
